flowchart TD
    Start([User visits Tesslate Studio]) --> CheckAuth{Authenticated?}

    CheckAuth -->|No| LoginPage[Show Login Page]
    CheckAuth -->|Yes| Dashboard[Show Dashboard]

    LoginPage --> ChooseMethod{Auth Method?}

    %% JWT Bearer Token Flow
    ChooseMethod -->|Email/Password| EmailLogin[Enter credentials]
    EmailLogin --> SubmitLogin[POST /api/auth/login]
    SubmitLogin --> ValidateCreds{Credentials<br/>valid?}

    ValidateCreds -->|No| LoginError[Show error message]
    LoginError --> LoginPage

    ValidateCreds -->|Yes| GenerateJWT[Generate JWT token:<br/>- user_id<br/>- email<br/>- role<br/>- exp: 7 days]
    GenerateJWT --> ReturnToken[Return:<br/>- access_token<br/>- token_type: bearer<br/>- user info]
    ReturnToken --> StoreToken[Store token in localStorage]
    StoreToken --> Dashboard

    %% OAuth Flow
    ChooseMethod -->|OAuth - GitHub| GitHubOAuth[Redirect to GitHub OAuth]
    ChooseMethod -->|OAuth - Google| GoogleOAuth[Redirect to Google OAuth]

    GitHubOAuth --> OAuthProvider[OAuth Provider Login Page]
    GoogleOAuth --> OAuthProvider

    OAuthProvider --> UserAuthorize{User<br/>authorizes?}

    UserAuthorize -->|No| OAuthCancel[Redirect to login<br/>with error]
    OAuthCancel --> LoginPage

    UserAuthorize -->|Yes| OAuthCallback[Redirect to callback:<br/>/api/auth/oauth/callback]

    OAuthCallback --> ExchangeCode[Exchange auth code<br/>for access token]
    ExchangeCode --> GetUserInfo[Fetch user profile<br/>from provider API]
    GetUserInfo --> CheckUserExists{User exists<br/>in DB?}

    CheckUserExists -->|No| CreateUser[Create User record:<br/>- email<br/>- oauth_provider<br/>- oauth_id]
    CheckUserExists -->|Yes| UpdateUser[Update last_login]

    CreateUser --> GenerateSessionJWT
    UpdateUser --> GenerateSessionJWT

    GenerateSessionJWT[Generate JWT token] --> SetCookie[Set HTTP-only cookie:<br/>- Name: tesslate_session<br/>- Domain: .your-domain.com<br/>- Secure: true<br/>- SameSite: Lax<br/>- Max-Age: 7 days]

    SetCookie --> StoreOAuthToken[Store OAuth credentials<br/>in DeploymentCredential table]
    StoreOAuthToken --> RedirectDashboard[Redirect to dashboard]
    RedirectDashboard --> Dashboard

    %% Cookie-based Session Flow
    ChooseMethod -->|Session Cookie| SessionAuth[Cookie sent automatically<br/>by browser]

    SessionAuth --> CheckCookie{Cookie<br/>valid?}

    CheckCookie -->|No| CookieError[Clear cookie]
    CookieError --> LoginPage

    CheckCookie -->|Yes| ExtractUserId[Extract user_id from JWT]
    ExtractUserId --> LoadUserSession[Load user from database]
    LoadUserSession --> Dashboard

    %% Authenticated Requests
    Dashboard --> MakeRequest[User makes API request]
    MakeRequest --> CheckAuthType{Auth Type?}

    CheckAuthType -->|Bearer Token| AddAuthHeader[Add header:<br/>Authorization: Bearer token]
    CheckAuthType -->|Session Cookie| SendCookie[Cookie sent automatically]

    AddAuthHeader --> APIMiddleware[FastAPI Middleware:<br/>Verify JWT]
    SendCookie --> APIMiddleware

    APIMiddleware --> VerifyJWT{JWT valid?}

    VerifyJWT -->|No - Expired| Return401[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    VerifyJWT -->|No - Invalid| Return401
    VerifyJWT -->|Yes| ExtractUser[Extract user from JWT]

    Return401 --> TriggerRefresh{Refresh<br/>available?}

    TriggerRefresh -->|No| ClearAuth[Clear auth state]
    ClearAuth --> LoginPage

    TriggerRefresh -->|Yes| RefreshToken[POST /api/auth/refresh]
    RefreshToken --> GenerateNewJWT[Generate new JWT token]
    GenerateNewJWT --> ReturnNewToken[Return new access_token]
    ReturnNewToken --> StoreToken
    StoreToken --> MakeRequest

    ExtractUser --> AttachToRequest[Attach user to request.state]
    AttachToRequest --> RouteHandler[Route handler executes]
    RouteHandler --> CheckPermissions{User has<br/>permission?}

    CheckPermissions -->|No| Return403[Return 403 Forbidden]
    CheckPermissions -->|Yes| ProcessRequest[Process request]

    ProcessRequest --> ReturnResponse[Return response]
    Return403 --> Dashboard
    ReturnResponse --> Dashboard

    %% CSRF Protection
    Dashboard --> CSRFCheck{POST/PUT/DELETE<br/>request?}
    CSRFCheck -->|Yes| GenerateCSRF[Generate CSRF token:<br/>Include in form/header]
    CSRFCheck -->|No| MakeRequest

    GenerateCSRF --> MakeRequest
    APIMiddleware --> ValidateCSRF{CSRF token<br/>valid?}
    ValidateCSRF -->|No| Return403
    ValidateCSRF -->|Yes| VerifyJWT

    %% Logout
    Dashboard --> LogoutAction{User clicks<br/>logout?}
    LogoutAction -->|Yes| ClearTokens[Clear localStorage token<br/>Clear session cookie]
    ClearTokens --> LoginPage

    %% Styling
    classDef startEnd fill:#4caf50,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#2196f3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#ff9800,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef error fill:#f44336,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#8bc34a,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef external fill:#9c27b0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    class Start,Dashboard startEnd
    class EmailLogin,SubmitLogin,GenerateJWT,ReturnToken,StoreToken,OAuthCallback,ExchangeCode,GetUserInfo,CreateUser,UpdateUser,GenerateSessionJWT,SetCookie,StoreOAuthToken,SessionAuth,ExtractUserId,LoadUserSession,MakeRequest,AddAuthHeader,SendCookie,APIMiddleware,ExtractUser,AttachToRequest,RouteHandler,ProcessRequest,GenerateNewJWT,ReturnNewToken,RefreshToken,GenerateCSRF,ClearTokens process
    class CheckAuth,ChooseMethod,ValidateCreds,UserAuthorize,CheckUserExists,CheckCookie,CheckAuthType,VerifyJWT,TriggerRefresh,CheckPermissions,CSRFCheck,ValidateCSRF,LogoutAction decision
    class LoginError,OAuthCancel,CookieError,Return401,Return403,ClearAuth error
    class RedirectDashboard,ReturnResponse success
    class GitHubOAuth,GoogleOAuth,OAuthProvider external
